OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain will
OL,6,Fstart heavy in places but will ease a
OL,7,Flittle tonight, but it will remain
OL,8,Fcloudy and mild with outbreaks of
OL,9,Fdrizzle. Winds will start light be
OL,10,Fstrengthen around coasts by dawn. Fog
OL,11,Fforming over the hills.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FA spell of heavy rain and
OL,14,Fblustery winds will move through on
OL,15,FWednesday morning, followed by drier
OL,16,Fand brighter weather with some
OL,17,Fshowers. Feeling warm in the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
