OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FChangeable over the next few days with
OL,7,Fspells of rain and showers at times.
OL,8,FBrighter interludes are likely too,
OL,9,Fand it will turn increasingly warm.
